Author: TaxiCashICO
Title: [ANN][ICO]TaxiCash is a new Blockchain based patented Taxi Payment Solution
Body: Yes access to GPS has now become available through API calls. Though civilian purpose GPS is accurate only to about 10m, it is more than sufficient for travel business purposes [similar to google maps etc]. Through a patented TaxiCashTM algorithm we are able to integrate GPS data into our TaxiCashTM auto wallet system. This will automatically calculate fares and complete the payment processing in driverless cars.  Note that this is a world first. No one yet devised a blockchain technology based auto payment system.

Author: TaxiCashICO
Title: [ANN][ICO]TaxiCash is a new Blockchain based patented Taxi Payment Solution
Body: The TaxiCashTM solution is patented and registered with Australian patent office. The solution is extremely suitable for micro-payments and the transaction costs are reduced by almost 15%. The transactions time is less than 10 seconds, which is mandatory for Taxi / Hire car/ Limousine industries.  The good aspect of TaxiCashTM solution is that it is scalable, can be used worldwide as Blockchain and mobile applications are universal. If one looks deep into this technology, it can now be used in any systems that accepts credit cards. The costs can be reduced by at least 10% overall.  The application of taxiCashTM to driver less cars may be 2-3 years away, but the developers have identified the potential and had the foresight to develop a solution that is world first.

Author: TaxiCashICO
Title: [ANN][ICO]TaxiCash is a new Blockchain based patented Taxi Payment Solution
Body: This is an interesting question in that as in any taxi / hire car / limousine travel transactions many mistakes are made. The blockchain entries cannot be changed, but we can make a journal correction and issue another transaction to rectify.  Both transactions can be seen on the blockchain. This is how errors will be dealt with.  Every transaction will have travel information included within modified QR code system. Again this is a patent specific activity. All information will be publicly available and receipts can be printed off the blockchain very easily.

Author: celofiguj
Title: [ANN][ICO]TaxiCash is a new Blockchain based patented Taxi Payment Solution
Body: TaxiCash   Summary of TaxiCash:  TaxiCash is a new Blockchain based patented Taxi Payment Solution to replace payments using traditional Credit and Debit Cards. This is a global taxi payment currency that would be accepted worldwide having no card payment fee or surcharges. TaxiCash is an Australian patented technology that will service a USD130 billion industry worldwide.  TaxiCash can be used in Taxis, hire cars and futuristic driver less cars. It is world first Blockchain application that integrates GPS technology to produce a scalable solution for world transport industry  A total of 80,000,000 tokens are issued for pre-sale and public sale, which is initially expected to service Australia, New Zealand, Singapore and Japan, which has a Taxi usage market more than USD 30 Billion. The tokens are sold at US$1.00 each initially, which implies a large premium would be expected on listing.  TaxiCash solution is highly scalable to other allied industries such as train, bus, plane transport areas as well as to any industries where majority of payments are made by Credit cards.
